Subject: [PATCH 3490/5965] usb: ftdi_sio: add Mindstorms EV3 console adapter
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

commit 67847baee056892dc35efb9c3fd05ae7f075588c upstream.

